# Energy Generation Analysis & Forecasting

## ðŸ“Œ Overview  
This project explores and forecasts energy generation, load, and price trends using historical time-series data. I perform data cleaning, feature engineering, model development, and visualization to uncover patterns and support planning decisions in the energy sector.

